elements.name: Login to Corporate Pulse Application

steps.name: Launch Corporate Pulse Application

I select the lbu in corporate pulse app
I enter "${employee.policy.login.GPA.OptionalBenefit.id}" email id in pulse app
I click on Submit button on app
